23/09/2005
BUCHAREST, Romania -- The DEMEX 05 military exercise involving Romanian ground forces wrapped up at the Cincu military grounds on Thursday (22 September). This was the most comprehensive exercise organised in Romania in the past five years, involving 3,000 officers and soldiers, 200 combat vehicles and 500 other vehicles. Its aim was to demonstrate the ability of land troops to conduct offensive and defensive combat actions in accordance with NATO standards. (Nine o'clock - 23/09/05; Rompres - 22/09/05)
